quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,101,"None mwanka iki mugihe musomerwa amajambo y’Imana matagatifu hamwe na y’intumwa y’Imana yuko iri kumwe namwe, n’uwufata Imana yiwe nka nkama, uyo muntu azoba yararongowe munzira igororotse"
  3,102,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimutinye Imana yanyu bimwe biboneka, kandi ntimuze musandabe atari uko mwabaye aba Isilamu b’ukuri"
  3,103,"Nimufatane k’umugozi w’Imana mwese uko\tmuri kandi ntimusanzarane, kandi mwibuke\timigisha y’Imana iri hejuru yanyu, mugihe mwari abansi kubandi nayo ica irahuza imitima yanyu kumigisha yayo nukuba mwese\tabavandimwe, kandi\tmwari\tkunkengera\ty’ikinogo\tc’umuriro\twa Jahannamu\tnayo\tica\tirabarokora\tnuwo\tmuriro, uko\trero\tniko\tImana ibabenyesha amajambo yayo matagatifu kugira ngo mushobore kurongoka"
  3,104,"Nihabe\tmuri mwebwe abantu\tbashikiriza\tubutumwa bw’amahoro hamwe n’abategeka abantu kugira ineza, hamwe n’ugutuza abantu kugira amabi, abo nabo nibo bantu bazoba batekaniwe"
  3,105,"Kandi ntimube nkabamwe bacanamwo n’ukutumvikana mugihe bashikirwa n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, nabo rero nibo bantu bazoba bafise ibihano biniya cane"
  3,106,"K’umusi waho amaso y’abantu azoba yera derere, n’ayandi maso azoba yirabura:- mbega mwoba mwarahakanye munyuma y’ukwemera kwanyu? rero nimuhonje ibihano kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu"
  3,107,"Nayo abazoba amaso yabo yera derere, ngaho mw’ijuru bazobayo mumigisha y’Imana abo bazobayo mubuzima bwabo bwose"
  3,108,"Aya niyo majambo y’Imana matagatifu tugusomera bimwe vy’ukuri, n’Imana ntikunda guhemukira ibiremwa vyiwe"